dil vil pyar vyar ( hindi : दिल विल प्यार व्यार ) is a 2002 bollywood romantic drama film featuring an ensemble cast led by r. madhavan , jimmy shergill and sanjay suri . the film was inspired by the songs of music composer r. d. burman and won positive reviews upon release in october 2002 . this film was dubbed into tamil as kettavarellam padalam .